for the additional duties of local authorities.
Mr Hunt condemned Labour's 'spend, spend, spend' approach, but failed to
secure a response when he challenged the Labour front bench to say whether
the demands for extra expenditure made by Mr Jones had been approved by Mr
John Smith, the shadow chancellor.
